.TH LINUXFM 1 "May 2026" "linux-file-manager 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
linuxfm \- lightweight PyQt6 file manager for Linux
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B linuxfm
.RI [ path ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B linuxfm
starts Linux File Manager, a lightweight graphical file manager written in
Python and PyQt6.
.PP
The application supports common file browsing workflows, bookmarks, trash
integration, previews, search, archive extraction, tagging, and a basic
hidden-folder vault.
.SH OPTIONS
The program currently accepts an optional path argument for future compatibility.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/linux-file-manager/config.json
User configuration file.
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/linux-file-manager/vault
Default hidden-folder vault location.
.SH AUTHOR
linux-file-manager contributors.
